---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing — SEOplant"
  description="SEOplant pricing: free open-source CLI, Cloud plans from $29/mo for programmatic SEO at scale, and Agency plans for teams managing 10+ sites."
>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 style="text-align:center;">Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
      <p style="text-align:center; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto var(--space-3xl); color:var(--color-text-muted);">
        Start free with open source. Upgrade when you need real SEO data, programmatic scale, or multi-site management.
      </p>

      <div class="grid cols-4" style="align-items:stretch;">
        <!-- Free -->
        <div class="card price-card">
          <h2>Open Source</h2>
          <div class="price">Free</div>
          <p class="desc">MIT License. Forever.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>5 pipeline modules (CLI)</li>
            <li>Heuristic SEO analysis</li>
            <li>Competitor crawling</li>
            <li>Astro site generation</li>
            <li>VPS/Vercel/Cloudflare deploy</li>
            <li>1 project</li>
            <li>Self-hosted dashboard</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/seoplant/seoplant" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width:100%;">GitHub Repo</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Starter -->
        <div class="card price-card">
          <h2>Starter</h2>
          <div class="price">$29<span>/mo</span></div>
          <p class="desc">Real data. AI writing.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in Free +</li>
            <li><strong>Real-time SEO data</strong></li>
            <li>AI content (10 articles/mo)</li>
            <li>Programmatic SEO (50 pages/mo)</li>
            <li>3 projects</li>
            <li>500 credits/month</li>
            <li>Hosted dashboard</li>
            <li>Email support (48h)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.seoplant.io/register" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width:100%;">Start Free Trial</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Pro -->
        <div class="card price-card featured">
          <div class="featured-badge">Most Popular</div>
          <h2>Pro</h2>
          <div class="price">$79<span>/mo</span></div>
          <p class="desc">Full power. Full scale.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in Starter +</li>
            <li><strong>Unlimited pSEO pages</strong></li>
            <li>AI content (100 articles/mo)</li>
            <li><strong>Rank monitoring</strong></li>
            <li>Content decay detection</li>
            <li>Auto-refresh suggestions</li>
            <li>10 projects</li>
            <li>2,000 credits/month</li>
            <li>Email support (24h)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.seoplant.io/register" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%;">Start Free Trial</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Agency -->
        <div class="card price-card">
          <h2>Agency</h2>
          <div class="price">$199<span>/mo</span></div>
          <p class="desc">For teams & agencies.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in Pro +</li>
            <li><strong>50 projects</strong></li>
            <li>500 AI articles/mo</li>
            <li>White-label reports</li>
            <li>Multi-client dashboard</li>
            <li>REST API access</li>
            <li>5,000 credits/month</li>
            <li>Priority Slack support</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://app.seoplant.io/register" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width:100%;">Get Started</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature Comparison -->
      <div style="margin-top:var(--space-3xl);">
        <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">Full Feature Comparison</h2>
        <div class="table-wrap">
          <table>
            <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Free</th><th>Starter</th><th>Pro</th><th>Agency</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>Projects</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>10</td><td>50</td></tr>
              <tr><td>SEO Data</td><td class="no">Heuristic</td><td class="yes">Real-time</td><td class="yes">Real-time</td><td class="yes">Real-time</td></tr>
              <tr><td>AI Content</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="yes">10/mo</td><td class="yes">100/mo</td><td class="yes">500/mo</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Programmatic SEO</td><td class="no">—</td><td>50 pages</td><td class="yes">Unlimited</td><td class="yes">Unlimited</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Rank Monitoring</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Decay Detection</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>One-click Deploy</td><td class="no">Manual</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>White-label</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>REST API</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="no">—</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Credits/month</td><td>100</td><td>500</td><td>2,000</td><td>5,000</td></tr>
              <tr><td>Support</td><td>Community</td><td>Email 48h</td><td>Email 24h</td><td>Slack</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div style="margin-top:var(--space-4xl);">
        <h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="grid cols-2" style="gap:var(--space-2xl);">
          <div>
            <h4>What counts as a "site"?</h4>
            <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">One domain with its own SEO strategy, design system, and deployment. Each site gets its own Astro project.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>What are AI credits?</h4>
            <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">Credits cover LLM API costs (content generation, strategy, analysis). 2,000 credits = ~100 articles or ~500 programmatic pages.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Can I export my site?</h4>
            <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">Yes. The generated site is a standard Astro project. You own the code. No lock-in. No proprietary format.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Do I need my own server?</h4>
            <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">No. You can deploy to Vercel (free tier), Netlify, or Cloudflare Pages. If you want your own VPS, we support that too.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>What's the difference from Byword or Surfer?</h4>
            <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">They generate content. We generate the entire site — SEO strategy, design, code, deployment — around that content.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Is the open source version limited?</h4>
            <p style="color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:0.9rem;">No artificial limits. It just doesn't include the paid data APIs, agent orchestration, or SaaS dashboard. All code is MIT.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .cols-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); }
  .cols-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); }
  .cols-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); }
  .price-card { text-align: center; padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-lg); }
  .price-card.featured { border: 2px solid var(--color-primary); transform: scale(1.03); position: relative; }
  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute; top: -14px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-primary); color: white; padding: 4px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
  }
  .price { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; margin: var(--space-md) 0 var(--space-xs); }
  .price span { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .desc { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .price-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; text-align: left; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }
  .price-card li { padding: 5px 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .price-card li::before { content: "+ "; color: var(--color-primary); font-weight: 700; }
  .table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  th, td { padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-surface); font-weight: 600; }
  td.yes { color: #059669; font-weight: 600; }
  td.no { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .price-card.featured { transform: none; }
  }
</style>
